$PROB 1001 phase1 1CMT $INPUT C ID TIME SEQ=DROP EVID AMT DV $DATA ../../data/derived/phase1.csv IGNORE=C $SUBROUTINE ADVAN2 TRANS2 $PK CL=THETA(1)*EXP(ETA(1)) V =THETA(2)*EXP(ETA(2)) KA=THETA(3)*EXP(ETA(3)) S2=V
$ERROR Y=F*EXP(ERR(1)) + ERR(2) IPRE=F
$THETA (10) ;CL (10) ;V (0.2) ;KA
$OMEGA 0.09 0.09 0.09 $SIGMA 0.09 0.1 $ESTIMATION MAXEVAL=9999 PRINT=5 NOABORT METHOD=1 INTER MSFO=./1001.msf $COV PRINT=E $TABLE NOPRINT FILE=./1001.tab ONEHEADER ID AMT TIME EVID PRED IPRE CWRES $TABLE NOPRINT FILE=./1001par.tab ONEHEADER ID TIME CL V KA ETA1 ETA2 ETA3
